library(cluster)
library(factoextra)
## Welcome! Want to learn more? See two factoextra-related books at https://goo.gl/ve3WBa
NEWcscoreClean <- NEWcscore %>% 
  select(-UNITID,-INSTNM)
NEWcscoreClean
## # A tibble: 843  3
##    ADM_RATE NPT4_PRIV ACTCM75
##       <dbl>     <dbl>   <dbl>
##  1    0.642     22994      29

##  8    0.962     12954      25
##  9    0.43      17473      20
## 10    0.351     28909      22
## #  with 833 more rows
NEWcscore2CL <- kmeans(NEWcscoreClean, centers = 2)
plot(NEWcscoreClean, col=NEWcscore2CL$cluster)

dis2CL = dist(NEWcscoreClean)^2
sil2CL = silhouette(NEWcscore2CL$cluster, dis2CL)
plot(sil2CL, col = NEWcscore2CL$cluster)

fviz_silhouette(sil2CL)
